data.description: Motivated sellers! Lovely 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home with RV parking boasting an array of features and potential in East Medford! The moment you step inside, you're greeted with a large and inviting living room with a cozy wood stove and beautiful brick surround. The kitchen offers ample cupboard and counter space, perfect for all of your culinary needs! As you explore further, you'll discover an additional space adjacent to the dining room, which could easily be utilized as a small family room or office space with a large slider leading to the backyard. One of the highlights of this property is the expansive fenced backyard with a delightful patio area, storage shed, and attached workshop, perfect for any project or additional storage! This home also has a newer roof! Location is everything, and this home has it all. Situated near schools, parks, and shopping centers, convenience is at your doorstep! Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your new home!
